Ensure to work in a Grid system as it allows you to bulid responsive web pages. container>row>cols
<hr> Used to have a horizontal rule.
We can a make a button that can have href
It can be done using <a href btn btn-primary>Sign</a>

bg-dark, bg-light, text-light, text-dark etc can also be there

To make a better displaying jumborton use
<div class="container">(this adds margin both to the left and right)
